11.2 다중 선형 회귀 수행하기

set.seed(42)
u <- rnorm(100)
v <- rnorm(100, mean = 3, sd = 2)
w <- rnorm(100, mean = -3, sd = 1)
e <- rnorm(100, mean = 0, sd = 3)
y <- 5 + 4 * u + 3 * v + 2 * w + e
lm(y ~ u + v + w)

best_pred <-
  as_tibble(pred) %>%
  select(-resp) |>
  map_dbl(cor, y = pred$resp) %>%
  sort(decreasing = TRUE) %>%
  .[1:4] %>%

  pred[.]
